1627
01:31:11,770 --> 01:31:15,513
There are a lot of,
uh, constructs around

1628
01:31:15,557 --> 01:31:19,778
who should be considered
native or indigenous

1629
01:31:19,822 --> 01:31:22,520
here in North America,

1630
01:31:22,564 --> 01:31:24,304
and this story
