1633
01:31:31,877 --> 01:31:33,531
We just don't get to see that
that often.

1634
01:31:33,575 --> 01:31:34,967
Truly, truly.

1635
01:31:35,011 --> 01:31:36,839
What are your thoughts
on representation

1636
01:31:36,882 --> 01:31:39,537
