the positive things,

1641
01:31:55,248 --> 01:31:57,250
and there are so many
wonderful things

1642
01:31:57,294 --> 01:31:58,817
that indigenous people do.

1643
01:31:58,861 --> 01:32:00,602
It speaks
to the misrepresentation

1644
01:32:00,645 --> 01:32:03,996
and the under-representation
of minorities.

1645
01:32:04,040 --> 01:32:06,085
I do think
that we're in a time

1646
01:32:06,129 --> 01:32:11,569
of racial reckoning and also
a historical acknowledgement

1647
01:32:11,613 --> 01:32:14,790
of how our country
got to the place

1648
01:32:14,833 --> 01:32:16,618
that we are in now.

1649
01:32:16,661 --> 01:32:18,402
The film shines a spotlight

1650
01:32:18,445 --> 01:32:21,231
on the themes of identity
and belonging.

1651
01:32:21,274 --> 01:32:24,060
How do you personally
define identity?

1652
01:32:24,103 --> 01:32:27,759
It's a lifetime journey
full of twists and turns

1653
01:32:27,803 --> 01:32:31,676
and one that is shaped
