1656
01:32:39,249 --> 01:32:42,208
since, uh,
since getting into Congress.

1657
01:32:42,252 --> 01:32:43,601
I have learned a lot.

1658
01:32:43,645 --> 01:32:45,647
I have seen
a lot of things

1659
01:32:45,690 --> 01:32:48,693
that I never would've seen
if I weren't in this position.

1660
01:32:48,737 --> 01:32:51,870
You know, there's constant
changes within your identity,

1661
01:32:51,914 --> 01:32:53,611
and as you grow,

1662
01:32:53,655 --> 01:32:55,787
